Draws the stack and the heap of a running Java program in 3D using
force-directed layout

Add a play and step button.

vm.suspend()
vm.createModificationWatchpointRequest(Field field) for every field of every object.
event.enable() every event

while (vm can run) {
    vm.resume()
    e = vm.eventQueue().remove()
    processEvent(e)
}
